      "message": "Benchmark                                   Time           CPU Iterations\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------\nBefore any of the changes\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/8        531889 ns     531863 ns       1182\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/16       544820 ns     544738 ns       1199\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/64       581810 ns     581631 ns       1199\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/256      548222 ns     548211 ns       1186\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/1024     540014 ns     539843 ns       1032\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/4k       535817 ns     535638 ns       1204\n\nWith the fix that caused the performance drop (down 15%)\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/8        623330 ns     623146 ns       1050\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/16       624205 ns     624108 ns       1052\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/64       617811 ns     617785 ns       1048\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/256      615192 ns     615104 ns       1064\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/1024     608118 ns     608030 ns        979\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/4k       607488 ns     607459 ns       1060\n\nWith this fix (up 10%)\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/8        538610 ns     538531 ns       1176\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/16       537475 ns     537253 ns       1186\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/64       537825 ns     537613 ns       1186\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/256      537780 ns     537717 ns       1185\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/1024     538253 ns     538174 ns       1187\nSkParagraphFixture/StylesBigO/4k       537711 ns     537672 ns       1184",
